measurements.description: Two dangling flowers and three buds on two inflorescences up to 62cm; dorsal sepal completely recurved into a tube, barely visible white background overlaid rose except basally; synsepal white marked marginally rose, more pronounced at the midrib and margin; petals twisted one quarter turn, white mostly overlaid rose, lighter at the lower margin; pouch full, white blushed rose frontally, spotted purple, sparse rose blothching internally; staminode hirsute, white overlaid rose, more strongly at margin; substance firm; texture matte.
